<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>مِقْدَارُ النَّفْلِ مِنْ الْغَنِيمَة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>التَّنْفِيلُ مِنْ الْغَنِيمَة بَعْدَ الْإِحْرَازِ فِي دَارِ الْحَرْب<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(مالك)</span> ,<span class="c5"> وَعَنْ سَعِيدِ بْنِ الْمُسَيَّبِ قَالَ:</span> كَانَ النَّاسُ يُعْطَوْنَ النَّفَلَ مِنْ الْخُمُسِ. <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) (ط) ٩٧٥ , (هق) ١٢٥٩٢</p> </div>